String
Logic version
9. Cross-Engine Contract Expectations
Engine
Usage Constraints
PIE
Must respect trust/confidence; no re-scoring
SIM
May recompute scenarios but not signals
DAT
Emits execution telemetry only
FLO
Financial signals are non-authoritative
DRE
Exploratory reads only
GGP
Audit and governance only
10. Field-Level Constraints & Validation
All timestamps UTC
Scores bounded [0,1]
JSON payloads schema-validated
IDs globally unique
11. Backward Compatibility Rules
Fields may be added, not removed
Field meaning must never change
Deprecated fields remain readable
12. Document Position in SIG Corpus
This DATADEF complements:
NS-SIG-007 — DATAMODEL
NS-SIG-006 — VERSION
It completes the SIG documentation set.
